OL,6,FA critical incident has been declared
OL,7,Fat Aneurin Bevan University Health
OL,8,FBoard after "sustained pressure" over
OL,9,Fthe last week.
OL,11,FThe health board said the critical
OL,12,Fincident was declared on Monday
OL,13,Fafternoon (13 January) as its services
OL,14,F"are currently experiencing
OL,15,Fexceptional demand due to a
OL,16,Fcombination of increased emergency
OL,17,Fattendances of very sick patients,
OL,18,Fhigh levels of winter virus infections
OL,19,Fon our wards, and an increase in the
OL,20,Fnumber of patients who are delayed in
OL,21,Fhospital awaiting discharge."
