OL,6,FIt has asked people to only attend
OL,7,Femergency departments if they have a
OL,8,Flife threatening illness or serious
OL,9,Finjury.
OL,11,FA spokesperson for Aneurin Bevan
OL,12,FUniversity Health Board said: "As a
OL,13,Fresult of sustained pressure and risk
OL,14,Fthroughout the hospital system over
OL,15,Fthe last week, we have declared a
OL,16,FCritical Incident this afternoon."
